org.corfudb.runtime.object

Interface ICorfuSMR<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the underlying object. Created by mwei on 11/10/16.

    public interface ICorfuSMR<T>
    The interface for an object interfaced with SMR.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static String CORFUSMR_SUFFIX
      The suffix for all precompiled SMR wrapper classes.
